      • isHidden

        boolean isHidden()
        Checks whether this type is hidden. If a type is hidden, its relations are not included in edge retrieval operations. Types used internally are hidden so they don't interfere with user types.
        Returns:
        true, if the type is hidden, else false.
        See Also:
        SystemType
